pyPfw06 module¶

pyPfw06.py_iauPfw06(double date1, double date2)¶

Wrapper for iauPfw06 module (SOFA Documentation.). For a given date, returns precession angles (Fukushima-Williams 4-angle formulation).

Parameters:
  • date1 (float) – Terrestrial Time as a 2-part Julian Date (Part 1).
  • date2 (float) – Terrestrial Time as a 2-part Julian Date (Part 2).
Returns:

(1x4) array containing:
  • gamb – F-W angle \(\overline{\gamma}\) (radians)
  • phib – F-W angle \(\overline{\phi}\) (radians)
  • psib – F-W angle \(\overline{\psi}\) (radians)
  • epsa – F-W angle \(\overline{\epsilon}\) (radians)
Return type:

(Numpy Array)
